    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739366",
        "quote": "I feel like people with their camera phones and Twitter and Facebook, this kind of question like, 'How can I be present and also document my presence or document what I'm doing?' is something that's always on my mind, even when I'm not working as a filmmaker.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739366"
        },
        "topics": [
