    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739340",
        "quote": "As far as the balance between being a journalist, being an artist, being a storyteller - documentary filmmakers are all three of those things. The balance between them is affected by the film itself, the topic of the film.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739340"
        },
