    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739343",
        "quote": "With 'Street Fight,' it took an urban mayoral election and found lots of complexity in there. The same with 'Racing Dreams.' I wanted to show complexity within this world that most documentary people don't know anything about.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739343"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Racing",
