                "url": "/topics/show"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739344",
        "quote": "When I'm making documentaries, I think a lot about how fiction films play. I want them to have the pacing, the twists and the character development of fiction films.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739344"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Think",
                "url": "/topics/think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Play",
                "url": "/topics/play"
            },
            {
                "name": "Films",
                "url": "/topics/films"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739345",
        "quote": "I'm not one of those people who sees documentaries as a stepping stone to doing fiction. I love documentaries and watch tons of documentaries. But, I like fiction films a lot, too.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739345"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Films",
                "url": "/topics/films"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739346",
        "quote": "After college, I did a bunch of different jobs - taught English in Mexico, worked in public radio, worked for a web design company - but there was something about documentaries that really attracted me.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739346"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "College",
                "url": "/topics/college"
            },
            {
                "name": "Jobs",
                "url": "/topics/jobs"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739347",
        "quote": "I'm not a purist - I like films that are narrated and films that aren't, films that are beautiful and films that are clumsy but heartfelt. Mostly, I just like a good story and good characters.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739347"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Good Story",
                "url": "/topics/good_story"
            },
            {
                "name": "Films",
                "url": "/topics/films"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mostly",
                "url": "/topics/mostly"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739348",
        "quote": "I think I'm drawn to people who dream big, and both films have that. In 'Street Fight, Cory Booker wants to become Mayor of Newark, and in 'Racing Dreams,' three kids want to become NASCAR drivers.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739348"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "I Think",
