    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739355",
        "quote": "The first time you watch a movie that you like, all of the magic works on you. It's an experience of having a world unfold in front of you. But if you watch it again, you start to see where the seams are.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739355"
