    {
        "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739357",
        "quote": "I think to many people the term 'activist film' implies a film with a single point of view - something designed to provoke outrage and urge action on a particular issue - sort of the film equivalent of a rally. 'If a Tree Falls' is not that kind of film.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Marshall Curry",
            "url": "/quotes/marshall_curry_739357"
        },
